00:47:09.510 --> 00:47:10.350
Atau...

00:47:11.920 --> 00:47:12.800
Saya akan lupakan dia.

00:47:19.960 --> 00:47:20.800
Chu Shan,

00:47:21.190 --> 00:47:22.510
mula mengemas barang saya hari ini.

00:47:24.590 --> 00:47:25.430
Ya, Jeneral.

